  <name>Skibiditop</name>
  <summary>Snappier Discord app with Vencord</summary>
  <developer_name>Vencord Contributors</developer_name>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">dev.papertobi.Skibiditop.desktop</launchable>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0</project_license>
  <project_group>Vencord</project_group>
  <description>
    <p>Skibiditop is a cross platform desktop app aiming to give you a snappier Discord experience with Vencord pre-installed.</p>
    <p>Skibiditop comes bundled with Venmic, a purpose-built library to provide functioning audio screenshare.</p>
  </description>
